59.9	Madrasah	Madrasah	Madrasah is the Arabic word (of Semitic origin; viz Hebrew midrash) for any type of educational institution, whether secular or religious (of any religion). It is variously transliterated as madrasah, madarasaa, medresa, madrassa, madraza, madarsa, medrese etc.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/44/MedresaVisoko.jpg/300px-MedresaVisoko.jpg
